    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and forged aluminum suspension components that maintain factory-spec geometry. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust; the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline with excellent compression across all cylinders. This is a mechanically sound, turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
